deps.context: AC_INIT([curl], [-], [a suitable curl mailing list: https://curl.se/mail/])

libs.content:
find_program (
      sphinx-${_sphinx_tool}_executable

      hints         "${sphinx_dir}"
      path_suffixes bin
      doc           "the sphinx-${_sphinx_tool} python script."

    )
